
Planned Parenthood provides education and health services to the general public about Contraception contraceptives, Pregnancy pregnancies, and sexually transmitted diseases/infections at little or no cost, depending on the service. You can get information about anything related to sex from them, condoms, and help during a pregnancy. Planned Parenthood also provides abortion services. More information, about their mission statement and policy http://www.plannedparenthood.org/pp2/portal/files/portal/aboutus/mission.xml can be read here. Be prepared to wait at least 1 and 1/2 hours past your appointment time. 
